* &quot;Stink&quot; (Twin/Tone) (1982)
* &quot;Hootenanny&quot; (Twin/Tone) (1983)
* &quot;Let It Be&quot; (Twin/Tone) (1984)
* &quot;Tim&quot; (Sire) (1985)
* &quot;Pleased to Meet Me&quot; (Sire) (1987)
* &quot;Don&#x27;t Tell a Soul&quot; (Sire) (1989)
* &quot;All Shook Down&quot; (Sire) (1990)

