==Twin towns – sister cities==
Tallinn is twinned with:

* Annapolis, United States
* Berlin, Germany
* Dartford, United Kingdom
* Ghent, Belgium
* Hangzhou, China
* Helsinki, Finland
* Kiel, Germany
* Kyiv, Ukraine
* Kotka, Finland
* Malmö, Sweden
* Odesa, Ukraine
* Beijing, China
* Riga, Latvia
* Schwerin, Germany
* Skopje, North Macedonia
* Tbilisi, Georgia
* Turku, Finland
* Venice, Italy
* Vienna, Austria
* Vilnius, Lithuania
